OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FPoliticians from the Scottish Borders
OL,7,Fhave welcomed the local authority's
OL,8,Fdecision to revisit its plans to close
OL,9,Ffive rural nurseries.
OL,11,FScottish Borders Council says it will
OL,12,Fnow look again at its plans to
OL,13,Ftemporarily close nurseries in
OL,14,FCockburnspath, Ednam, Oxton, Yetholm
OL,15,Fand Walkerburn for the 2025/26
OL,16,Feducation year.
