OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FAs planned, nurseries currently under
OL,7,Fmothballed status in Spouston,
OL,8,FWestruther and Fountainhall will
OL,9,Fcontinue to be reviewed through
OL,10,Fconsultation with parents in those
OL,11,Fcommunities.
OL,13,FLast month, Scottish Borders Council
OL,14,Fvoted to proceed with plans to close
OL,15,Fthe nurseries, citing a reduction in
OL,16,Fthe number of children using the
OL,17,Ffacilities and the need to save money.
OL,19,FMore than 30 parents in Cockburnspath,
OL,20,Fnear Eyemouth, took part in a protest
OL,21,Fagainst the proposals on 2 May 2025.
