OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FThe council now says different models
OL,7,Fwill be considered in order to keep
OL,8,Fearly years education accessible
OL,9,Facross the area, at the next full
OL,10,Fcouncil meeting on 9 May 2025.
OL,12,FThe motion to be discussed proposes
OL,13,Fthat early learning and childcare
OL,14,Fprovisions at Channelkirk,
OL,15,FCockburnspath, Ednam, Walkerburn and
OL,16,FYetholm are maintained in the 2025/26
OL,17,Facademic year, with possible changes
OL,18,Fto the way the services are provided.
