OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FJohn Lamont, MP for Berwickshire,
OL,7,FRoxburgh and Selkirk, says councillors
OL,8,F"still need to go further" to
OL,9,Fguarantee the future of early learning.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's very welcome that the
OL,12,Fcouncil have u-turned and decided
OL,13,Fagainst closing several nurseries.
OL,15,F"Parents rely on them, and it would be
OL,16,Fa major inconvenience if they were to
OL,17,Fshut or hours were to be substantially
OL,18,Freduced.
