OL,6,F"I said the local authority needed to
OL,7,Freconsider these plans from the start
OL,8,Fand I will continue to encourage the
OL,9,Fcouncil to protect essential rural
OL,10,Fservices."
OL,12,FMSP for Ettrick, Roxburgh and
OL,13,FBerwickshire, Rachael Hamilton,
OL,14,Fbelieves "parents' views must be
OL,15,Fsought on the new proposals".
