OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FShe said: "I made it clear the
OL,7,Foriginal plans were unacceptable, so I
OL,8,Fam pleased to see the council have now
OL,9,Faccepted that; however, there are
OL,10,Fstill clear issues that need to be
OL,11,Faddressed before integrating nursery
OL,12,Fand school provision.
OL,14,F"We should be looking to expand
OL,15,Fchildcare options for parents, not
OL,16,Flimit them.
OL,18,F"I will continue to campaign for these
OL,19,Fnurseries to remain open and available
OL,20,Fto parents when they need help."
