OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,FScottish Borders Councillor Julie
OL,7,FPirone, Executive Member for
OL,8,FEducation, Youth Development and
OL,9,FLifelong Learning, says potential
OL,10,F"solutions" have been developed after
OL,11,Flistening to "many voices on our very
OL,12,Fsmall nursery provision".
OL,14,FShe said: "These continue to put the
OL,15,Feducational experience of our children
OL,16,Fat the heart of everything we do and
OL,17,Fare a potential way forward for 2025/
OL,18,F26.
