OL,3,CPoliticians welcome council's U-turn
OL,4,Con closure of nurseries
OL,6,F"Removing the prospect of mothballing
OL,7,Fin the next year also provides some
OL,8,Fcertainty for children and parents/
OL,9,Fcarers and allows for further work and
OL,10,Fengagement on our mothballing policy.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank everyone who
OL,13,Fhas engaged with the council over the
OL,14,Flast few weeks and given helpful views
OL,15,Fto allow us to come up with potential
OL,16,Fsolutions, which I believe will work
OL,17,Fin our small rural committees and
OL,18,Fwhich answers many of the questions
OL,19,Fasked of us."
